//    +-------+     +------+       +----------+       +---------+       +---------+       +---------+
//    |BEGIN  |---->| IDLE |------>| PREARMED |------>| ARMED   |------>| RUNNING |------>|   STOP  |
//    +-------+     +------+       +----------+       +---------+       +---------+       +---------+    
//                       ^              |                   |                 |                 |                          
//                       |              |                   |                 |                 |                         
//                       +--------------+<------------------+<----------------+<----------------+
//
